{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"990c25efe5","title":"在上海听取整风情况汇报时的指示（摘录）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cf13d2a7b1","index":0,"year":1957,"month":9,"day":17,"articleId":"990c25efe5"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui3","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1949-1957卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui3a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"362ee5d1c2","type":"title","text":"在上海听取整风情况汇报时的指示（摘录）","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"990c25efe5"},{"id":"44f0c13389","type":"paragraph","text":"要青年学生打杂扫地，也不是一件坏事啊！我看对青年一定得加强思想政治工作，要教育青年不再轻视劳动，要愿意参加体力劳动，才能建设好我们的国家！","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"990c25efe5"},{"id":"a38cbccd34","type":"paragraph","text":"青年，即使是青年工人，因为没有受过旧社会的苦，更应该加强阶级教育，提高他们的思想觉悟。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"990c25efe5"},{"id":"70544f109a","type":"paragraph","text":"（摘自《毛主席关怀我们》一文，《中国青年》一九五八年第二十二期）","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"990c25efe5"}],"page":{"id":"4f8ec676bb","publicationId":"wansui3","articleId":"990c25efe5","start":440,"end":440}}}},"__N_SSG":true}